The paper discusses reinforcement learning algorithms and their effectiveness on continuous control tasks, specifically on the Linear Quadratic Regulator (LQR). This falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), control systems (cs.SY), robotics (cs.RO), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
